data.title: Metta World Peace has made a big difference on the Lakers since Byron Scott FINALLY decided to play him...He should've listened to me earlier!
data.meta_description: Metta World Peace Leads the Lakers to their first Victory Both Scott and Kobe attributed their first win to Metta's defense. The comments post game from Metta were hysterical, apologizing to TWC Sportsnet for his unshaven face.
